- Abadi et al., "Materialization Strategies in a Column-Oriented DBMS", ICDE 2007
- ClickHouse: `src/Processors/QueryPlan/Optimizations/optimizeLazyMaterialization.cpp`
- Boncz et al., "MonetDB/X100: Hyper-Pipelining Query Execution", CIDR 2005
